<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Friday,
Sept. 17. If you have any questions, please call The Star's Melanie
Gray at (816) 234-4778.
</P>
<P>
   JAZZ-MAHOGANY-KANSAS (KANSAS CITY, Mo.) _ Just six years ago,
Kevin Mahogany supported himself by working as a data processor
while pursuing a dream: to be a jazz singer. In nightclubs all over
