</P>
<P>
   Price as tested: $28,225
</P>
<P>
   Horsepower/Torque: 160 hp/ 170 lb.-ft.
</P>
<P>
   Wheelbase/Overall length: 100.4 inches/ 176.4inches
</P>
<P>
   Width/Height: 67.7 inches/ 55.5 inches
</P>
<P>
