wholesale plans to bring expats home, because we don't see the need
for that,'' she said.
</P>
<P>
   Hallman said plant managers in foreign countries often face
power outages, phone failures and other difficulties. ``Many of
them have been in situations where they have been
</P>
</TEXT>
