certainly from New Jersey through the five boroughs and around to
New England, Floyd fixated millions of people yesterday, staring at
some from television screens with its Cyclopian eye etched in
synthetic orange swirls and blasting others right in the face with
potent rainy gusts. By Andrew C. Revkin.
</P>
