opposition to clemency granted by President Clinton to a group of
FALN activists. (Shana Raab/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) ROXBURY, Mass. -- Sept. 16, 1999 -- HURRICANE-FLOYD-1,
09-16 -- Participants in the Boston to New York AIDS fund-raising
bike ride wait to load their bikes onto trucks in a parking lot at
Northeastern University. The first leg of the ride was cancelled
due to weather associated with Hurricane Floyd. Bikes and riders
will be transported to Connecticut where they hope resume their
ride Friday morning. (George Rizer/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
