<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEXAS-SHOOTING-BUSH-325&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BUSH BLAMES `WAVE OF EVIL' FOR SHOOTINGS ACROSS NATION 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Mich.)  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also sent with `p' code) 
(See also TEXAS-SHOOTING, TEXAS-SHOOTING-SCENE) 
 (bl)  
